member.name: T:BookWorm.Construct.ConstructNumberFormat.NumberFormatType
member.summary:
The number format of the cell. In this documentation the locale is assumed to be en_US, but the actual format depends on the locale of the spreadsheet.
TEXT - Text formatting, e.g 1000.12. NUMBER - Number formatting, e.g, 1,000.12. PERCENT - Percent formatting, e.g 10.12%. CURRENCY - Currency formatting, e.g $1,000.12. DATE - Date formatting, e.g 9/26/2008. TIME - Time formatting, e.g 3:59:00 PM. DATE_TIME - Date+Time formatting, e.g 9/26/08 15:59:00. SCIENTIFIC - Scientific number formatting, e.g 1.01E+03.
